Interface FireStationNotificationCI

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface FireStationNotificationCI
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.OfferedCI, fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.RequiredCI, FireStationNotificationImplI
    The component interface FireStationNotificationCI defines the notifications that can be sent by a fire station.

    Invariant

     invariant      true
